body_text:
You can use Promise.resolve as a shorthand for this:
getItem(key) {
    return Promise.resolve(localStorage.getItem(this._key(key));
}

body:
You can use [`Promise.resolve`](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise/resolve) as a shorthand for this:

``` javascript
getItem(key) {
    return Promise.resolve(localStorage.getItem(this._key(key));
}
```
